{
  "stem": "14867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had three entrances.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was-- one was a formal, and one was coming in to-- to a foyer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Another one was coming through a little hole to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my-- my grandmother lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had an apartment for her and her daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there was another apartment for another aunt, my mother's sister, who had a family with three children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then there was a little apartment for the servants who lived downstairs-- and a big laundry also downstairs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And anytime my father would come for Friday-- usually it would be Friday-- my mother would be dressed in her best clothes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and I remember always she had wavy hair, always her hair washed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we always teased her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Aha, father is coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All week you are sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You're not feeling well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now you're feeling wonderful, and you're dressed up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She said that's how you have to be when you're expecting your husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember that she always catered to my husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish, and Polish, and Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's secretary was Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So because he was from the intelligentsia, and he didn't like the Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was really very aristocratic in Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most of our peasant servants were Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you really had to know Russian Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, we-- my parents and my grandparents spoke a lot of Yiddish, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was really fun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And any time my father was coming, we heard already the horse or the trot of the horses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all ran out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so it was really a very-- it was a beautiful childhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'll tell you, a lot of things I don't even remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
